thread.title: Andrew & Brooke
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Andrew & Brooke

author: Andrew & Brooke
title: Andrew & Brooke
text:
We can highly recommend Michael Keogh from Nelson Alexander. His professional approach and industry knowledge was outstanding.
Michael always kept us informed and up to date on the progress of the campaign, which resulted in an excellent result for us.
This is the second time we have used Michael and would not hesitate to use him again on any future business.
